Transifex.net
=============

The website transifex.net

Dependencies
------------

* Transifex is developed on top of Django. Install Django using the 
  install package tool of your system or just download it from:
  http://www.djangoproject.com/
   
* Some of the dependencies can be installed by using easy_install:
  ``easy_install markdown python-openid httplib2 ...``

* All the others application denpendencies can be downloaded from 
  http://code.google.com/p/<application name> and then installed by 
  using the setup.py or creating a symbolic link as following:

  * django-tagging (python setup.py install)
  * django_authopenid (python setup.py install)
  * django-pagination (create a symbolic link in your PYTHONPATH)
  * django-contact-form (python setup.py install)

  * For notifications (it's optional):
   - django-notification (create a symbolic link in your PYTHONPATH)
   - http://django-atompub.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/atompub/atom.py
     (download it and rename to atomformat.py and put it somewhere in 
     your PYTHONPATH)

Installing Transifex
--------------------

* Customize ``settings.py`` and ``urls.py``.
* Run ``./manage.py syncdb``
* Run ``./manage.py runserver 8088``.

To enable debugging, run the server as follows:

``./manage.py runserver --settings settings_debug``  

Testing
-------

``./manage.py test``